{"tid":776243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"按摩店男技師summer: 囗爆800 打J 600","createTime":"2018-08-12T00:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T01:48:43.000Z","uid":72009,"like":33,"dislike":108,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"592d824c37bd9ff290e4d2c2728cbe494b9fa6fa","tid":776243,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T00:25:55.000Z","msg":"記者表示要光顧90分鐘一般按摩服務後，便獲安排進入其中一間約100平方呎房間，四周被黑窗簾包圍，內有一個日式透明企缸，房間幾乎無光，但有彩燈不停變換顏色，加強情調，旁邊有一張已鋪上大毛巾的按摩床、一張單人梳化，主持人先後安排3名技師供記者過目。<br />\n<br />\n記者最終揀選21歲技師Summer，身形矮瘦的他身穿T恤，手持按摩油及10多張紙巾等進來，之後直接推銷服務稱可幫忙口交，「收費800元，全身按摩加handjob(手淫)就600元，你想要什麼？」他續稱，若客人只選擇按摩，他們一毫子也無法分，只有客人光顧色情服務，他們才能全數賺取相關收費，「客人不做(色情)，我們就無錢分，無底薪，有時空等一日無錢。」<br />\n<br />\n他自稱本身從事飲食業，每周兼職來上班2天，高峰時每日可接2至3個客，日搵2,000多元，「但有時一日無兩個客，有時食白果，不一定的，可能現在不旺場。」不過他透露自己喜歡男性，也喜歡此工作，「雖然賺錢唔多，但幫補吓，我剛考到牌半年，平時愛揸車，當幫補吓車嘅使費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180811/58551370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180811%2F58551370&d=OPdEuTM8pvrXw7khawfK%2BJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8554f552\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180811%2F58551370&h=f2c2b60d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180811/58551370</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180811/large/1533987913_bf2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180811%2Flarge%2F1533987913_bf2a.jpg&h=2fa14dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180811/large/1533987913_bc51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180811%2Flarge%2F1533987913_bc51.jpg&h=f8cf18e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class